snippet.title: Frostpunk 2 | City Unbound Compilation
snippet.description:
#Frostpunk 2 is coming on September 20th. Pre-order the Digital Deluxe Edition now and get 3 days early access and more: http://re.11bits.com/m26

City Unbound is a series focused on showing all the different facets and features of the upcoming Frostpunk 2 🧊 Here's a recap of all eight episodes, featuring swift highlights for your viewing pleasure.
